author: jdcasey
msg: [MASSEMBLY-113][MASSEMBLY-106] Verified proper behavior when '..' directory is used in a fileSet, and added ability to specify <attachmentClassifier/> element in <binaries/> under a module set. When the classifier is specified, any module in that set that doesn't have a matching attachment will cause the assembly to fail. Otherwise, the attached artifact is used instead of the project artifact.
